Artsphere Studio Application.

Overview
This Artsphere Studio Application is a dynamic web application that allows users to browse, search, and manage a collection of artworks. Built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, it features full CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) functionality powered by json-server as a mock backend API.

