Usage Guide
Browsing Artworks
View all artworks in the main gallery

Click on any artwork to see detailed view

Use the search bar to filter artworks

Adding New Artwork
Click "Add New Art" button

Fill out the form with artwork details

Click "Save" to add to the gallery

Editing Artwork
Click "Edit" button on any artwork card

Modify the details in the form

Click "Save" to update

Deleting Artwork
Click "Delete" button on any artwork card

Confirm deletion in the dialog